text: Gunabati Railway Station Foot Over Bridge Gunabati Railway Station () is located in the heart of Gunabati Bazar. The station is the main station of Gunabati Union and is linked to Dhaka by the Gunabati – Cumilla rail line, to Chattagram by the Gunabati – Feni line. ==References== Category:Railway stations in Comilla District
title: Gunabati Railway Station
